Regulation (EC) No 504/2007 is amended as follows:
1. in Article 2 paragraph 3 is replaced by the following:
2. the introductory phrase of the first paragraph of Article 3 is replaced by the following:
3. Article 4 is replaced by the following:
(a) the purchasing contract or any other equivalent document;
(b) the insurance contract;
(c) the invoice;
(d) the certificate of origin (where applicable);
(e) the transport contract;
(f) and, in the case of sea transport, the bill of lading.
4. Annex I is amended as follows:
(a) in the first column:
— code 0402 91 11 is replaced by code 0402 91 10,
— code 0402 91 31 is replaced by code 0402 91 30,
— code 0402 99 11 is replaced by code 0402 99 10;
(b) the codes 0402 91 19 and 0402 91 39, and the data related to those codes, are deleted.
